003package es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.emptyfiltering;
004
005import java.util.Set;
006
007import es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.entity.ProcessedDocument;
008import es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.AbstractProcessingStep;
009import es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.ProcessingStepService;
010import es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.emptyfiltering.entity.NonEmptyTextDocument;
011import es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.emptyfiltering.entity.NonEmptyTextWithTitleDocument;
012import es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.emptyfiltering.xml.definition.IncludeRedditDeletedProcessingStepParameter;
013import es.uvigo.esei.sing.textproc.step.xml.definition.AbstractProcessingStepParameter;
014
015/**
016 * The service implementation for this processing step.
017 *
018 * @author Alejandro González García
019 */
020public final class EmptyFilteringProcessingStepService implements ProcessingStepService {
021        @Override
022        public AbstractProcessingStep create() {
023                return new EmptyFilteringProcessingStep();
024        }
025
026        @Override
027        public String getName() {
028                return "EmptyFiltering";
029        }
030
031        @Override
032        public Set<Class<? extends AbstractProcessingStepParameter>> getAdditionalParameters() {
033                return Set.of(IncludeRedditDeletedProcessingStepParameter.class);
034        }
035
036        @Override
037        public Set<Class<? extends ProcessedDocument>> getProcessedDocumentTypes() {
038                return Set.of(NonEmptyTextDocument.class, NonEmptyTextWithTitleDocument.class);
039        }
040}
